metadata.name: Kither- F*CK THAT (Kloud9-Dream)
metadata.description:
Genesis Mint: F*CK THAT!

        Post 3 years writers block... 3 years depression
        a true coming of age.
        i had a need to fit in, i compromised myself, was lost in the process.
        i found what works for me
        beyond doubt.
        beyond fitting in.
        An Ode to continue the march Onwards thru times of distress :
        Remember Mind Over Matter

        Never let go of your dreams, always have fun.
